person who has no respect for oth-
ers. . ,
And don’t think this does not
affect the public’s perception of
Webber and his Wolverine team-
mates. When you hear people talk
about Michigan it is usually some-
thing to this effect; “I hate Michigan
 I’rn glad they lost” or “they’re a
bunch of punks  they play gangsta
ball.” Now if they were ﬁve talented
white kids from suburbia, would
Michigan take all the ﬂack it has
received this season as supposed

