Carmela Mariani placed 14th and
Melanie Ishman finished 16th.

Lewis said he considers
Dogwood and this week’s
Panther Relays to be a “final
check” on the team’s perfor-
mance before it travels to its
toughest meet of the year, the
Penn Relays. The team will be
aiming for more than first-place,
finishes this weekend.

